{
  "stem": "6526.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We came over, and we saw the shots and this was the time when-- And how long did you remain in--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we remained there-- the funeral was on a Sunday.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They did not allow, but a lot of-- the Germans left already.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the funeral, everybody went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to bury him in the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a lot of people went from different places around to the funeral.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when we came back, I think it was a Tuesday.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The funeral was on Monday, if I'm not mistaken.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yes, the funeral was a Monday, because the following day, we were sitting Shivah.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we heard that the Germans are going to come soon to send us out to labor camps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's what they called them, because although Treblinka was not far from us, we didn't know it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't know that Treblinka existed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it was so quietly, and everybody was afraid to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And a few days later, they took us out all on the square in the market to send us to Treblinka with wagons to the train.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The train was 5 kilometers from us, Mrozy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I took some pails to bring in water from the river to help out the people were sitting in the market.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "A few times I went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then I saw it was getting closer to evening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They're going start moving out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I did not come back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I had a friend with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We both hid in a stall, looking out and see what's happening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A stall, horse.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, a stall, a horse stall.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Stall, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were there looking out and see what happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
